            <SHORT_DESCR>
               <P>This is a contract for bogie repair, wheelset overhaul and wheel re-profiling for the current Subway rolling stock fleet to Wabtec Rail Limited.</P>
            </SHORT_DESCR>
            <VAL_TOTAL CURRENCY="GBP" PUBLICATION="YES">705790</VAL_TOTAL>
            <NO_LOT_DIVISION/>
            <OBJECT_DESCR ITEM="1">
               <n2016:NUTS CODE="UKM82"/>
               <MAIN_SITE>
                  <P>SPT Broomloan Depot,</P>
                  <P>Robert Street, Glasgow.</P>
                  <P>G51 3HB.</P>
               </MAIN_SITE>
               <SHORT_DESCR>
                  <P>This is for the award of a contract for bogie repair, wheelset overhaul and wheel re-profiling for the current Subway rolling stock fleet to to Wabtec Rail Limited.</P>
               </SHORT_DESCR>
               <NO_OPTIONS/>
               <NO_EU_PROGR_RELATED/>
            </OBJECT_DESCR>
         </OBJECT_CONTRACT>
         <PROCEDURE>
            <DIRECTIVE_2014_25_EU>
               <PT_AWARD_CONTRACT_WITHOUT_CALL>
                  <D_OUTSIDE_SCOPE/>
                  <D_JUSTIFICATION>
                     <P>Bogie repairs.</P>
                     <P>The rolling stock power bogies are now nearing end of operational life and have required specialist repairs over a number of years. All previous specialist repairs have been completed by Wabtec. Wabtec has been involved, with SPT, in how any crack repairs are undertaken and hold the process documentation methodology and design liability for the repairs. Wabtec also hold the specialised jigs which enable the bogies to be welded and inspected on completion to ensure bogies are returned to SPT within design tolerances without distortion. Wabtec has a proven, reliable supply chain which ensures efficient approved weld preparation work.</P>
                     <P>Wheel and Wheelset Services.</P>
                     <P>SPT wheel size and gauge is unique. Wabtec has the only wheel lathe in Scotland which is capable of re-profiling these wheels. Wabtec recently committed to maintaining this equipment to ensure SPT has this continued support to end of current fleet life.</P>
                     <P>Wabtec has the experience and skill to check and overhaul wheel bearings and measure axle wear and replace as necessary. Wabtec has gained the experience, skills and knowledge to complete this work over many years. This extensive experience ensures only items which need to be replaced are; this enables SPT wheelsets to be repaired in a safe, efficient and economical manner.</P>
                  </D_JUSTIFICATION>
               </PT_AWARD_CONTRACT_WITHOUT_CALL>
            </DIRECTIVE_2014_25_EU>
